Someone who looks like me was using my car and licenceMakhene was allegedly nabbed in Bramley, Johannesburg, for drunk driving in 2015.But the actress, singer and sangoma maintains her innocence, saying someone known to her was driving using her documents.She, however, did not reveal the identity of the person."Someone who looks like me was using my car and licence, and that person has since been admitted to a mental institution."Makhene said the person looks like her but refused to divulge if it was one of her sisters or close relatives. "This is a personal matter and you are digging up for things that will hurt a lot of people, but I know you don't care," she said.According to Bramley police spokesman Molefe Mogodi the case was opened at the station. He said the matter was resolved in court.